dct_title_s: Cram's detailed radio map of the United States & Canada
dct_description_sm: Inset map: North America. Scale 1 in.=600 mi. Relief shown in hachures. Cover title: Radio map of the United States, published by the George F. Cram Company for Morton Salt Company ... revised to Dec. 5 1926. Shows time zones. Includes listings of radio stations by place and by call letters. Includes advertisement for Morton's Salt.
